body:
AvM Modpack: Step into the world of "Animation vs. Minecraft" and wield the iconic items and powerful staffs used by the legendary Stick Figures! This mod brings the action-packed battles and magical abilities from the famous animated series right into your Minecraft world. Use staffs to unleash elemental powers like fire, lightning, and ice, or craft unique items that give you special abilities and effects. Whether you want to recreate epic scenes or forge your own adventures, the AvM Modpack lets you experience the series like never before. Unleash your inner animator and bring the Stick Figures' power to life! ⚔️✨

If you want the AvM Pigstep, go to this site! {It may or may not work}

[https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/avm-remixed-pigstep/](https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/avm-remixed-pigstep/)
